entries.journal_entry_description: Deliver the contraband to the fence in the allotted time.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Alec in the allotted time.  For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Quinton in the allotted time.  For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Dreda in the allotted time.  For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Tylar in the allotted time.  Tylar is located on Dathomir. For this assignment you will have to launch into space and hyperspace to the Dathomir system.  If you try to travel directly using your ship the authorities are sure to catch you.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Alwynn in the allotted time. Alwynn is located on Rori. For this assignment you will have to launch into space and hyperspace to the Rori system.  If you try to travel directly using your ship the authorities are sure to catch you.
entries.task07_comm_message_text: I was told your skills at this were almost unmatched, perhaps that was bad information.  At any rate, shape up, or I will not deal with you further.
